description:
The finale of Love is Blind: Germany: Season 2 is expected to release on Netflix on January 15, 2026. 

This market will resolve according to the listed couples who are pronounced married by the end of the final episode of Love is Blind: Germany: Season 2. The reunion episode will not be taken into account. 

If the listed couple definitively splits or is otherwise not married by the end of the final episode of Love is Blind: Germany: Season 2, this market will resolve to "No".

If the season finale is not released or is definitively cancelled by February 15, 2026, 11:59PM ET, this market will resolve to "No couples marry".

The resolution source for this market will be the finale episode of Love is Blind: Germany: Season 2, or a consensus of credible reporting.
